snippet.title: Launch Announcement | Cinematic Trailer - Legends of Runeterra
snippet.description:
Can’t wait? Get the game and play RIGHT NOW at https://playruneterra.com. Official launch on PC and Mobile coming April 30.

Join the community and see more: 
WEBSITE: https://playruneterra.com   
DISCORD: https://discord.gg/legendsofruneterra      
YOUTUBE: you are here
TWITCH: https://twitch.tv/riotgames    
INSTAGRAM: https://instagram.com/legendsofruneterra   
TWITTER: https://twitter.com/playruneterra  
FACEBOOK: https://facebook.com/legendsofruneterra

Video created in partnership with Unit Image
https://www.unit-image.fr/ 
Directed by Ben Hibon
